Source: wrkmon
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Umar Khan Yousafzai <ionkhan@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), python3, python3-pip, python3-venv
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/Umar-Khan-Yousafzai/Wrkmon-TUI-Youtube

Package: wrkmon
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.10), mpv
Description: Stealth TUI YouTube audio player
 wrkmon is a terminal-based YouTube audio player that runs completely
 hidden in the background. Stream music while looking productive!
 .
 Features:
  - Search and stream YouTube audio
  - No visible windows - completely stealth
  - TUI interface with keyboard controls
  - Queue management with shuffle/repeat
  - Play history and playlists
